{"tid":602820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"圍毆兼剝少年褲 4青年收監","createTime":"2018-03-23T08:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T08:45:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8bea12a12c40c6e7e1a40960f0e6ee9aa13d9f42","tid":602820,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:37:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180323/20340372\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F20340372&d=hNXgKv16K%2FAoYbsNLvoNVW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=62fd017e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F20340372&h=3cbb7868\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180323/20340372</a><br />\n<br />\n圍毆兼剝少年褲<br />\n4青年收監<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180323/large/18478800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180323%2Flarge%2F18478800.jpg&h=91477fd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事主黃阡碩早前曾出庭作供。　資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】16歲少年前年除夕與人口角，去年1月晚應約到藍田公園，遭10名惡少圍毆及以金屬棒擊頭致失去知覺，復被剝褲，下體僅被一塊葉遮蔽。4名早前認罪的青年昨被判監21至28個月，法官明言已寬大處理，並寄語：「希望輕判係幫助而唔係害咗你哋！我唔希望再喺法庭犯人欄度見到你哋！」各被告向法官道謝。<br />\n<br />\n法官指本案案情嚴重，幸事主最後完全康復；考慮被告有悔意，已拘押14個月，若判教導所將無助他們更生。法官指，唯一用鐵通向事主黃阡碩施襲的李銘東，罪責最重，判監28個月；曾頂證其他被告的王壠澤判囚21個月；徐寶軒和譚建榮則入獄26個月。4人年齡介乎16至18歲。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC381/17<br />\n■記者蔡少玲"},{"pid":"27c207ab34fa494bf56eaa59729bafe688d01943","tid":602820,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解影到個事主好似好奸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aae20ea476deb6a428b0506fdc8527a5036c19e","tid":602820,"uid":30214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27c207ab34fa494bf56eaa59729bafe688d01943","tid":602820,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解影到個事主好似好奸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:43:48.000Z","msg":"換到幾條友坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f0656033e73cd96c0bffb192c2cba7f5622eff","tid":602820,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27c207ab34fa494bf56eaa59729bafe688d01943","tid":602820,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解影到個事主好似好奸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/GQ4WkuBl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGQ4WkuBl.jpg&h=9893724c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}